Sampdoria, Prad&egrave;: &quot;Milan asked us for authorization to speak to Strinic&quot;<br />
<br />
Sampdoria director Daniele Prad&egrave; spoke after the game against Milan: &quot;I can confirm that Milan asked us for authorization to speak to Strinic. Ivan is an exemplary professional. We are not excluding anything, as he will be our player until June 30. Renewal? Certainly, we will do it, let's see what happens.&quot;

Pirlo: &quot;On May 21 at San Siro I will play my farewell match which I would like to share with everyone. I chose San Siro because it's where I played the most of my career and met many of my teammates, but it's also for a logistic matter for those coming from abroad.&quot;<br />
<br />
Pirlo: &quot;Milan? In red &amp; black I started playing at high levels. Thanks to the arrival of Ancelotti we have won everything.&quot;
